新东方进入 K12 市场，最初仅面向中小学生提供英语辅导，2008 年推出全科辅导。 这也是「双减」落地后，新东方创始人俞敏洪首次公开露面。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-22ad74a95a4b0774b93ac1257a4adb4c_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "297 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/489244809"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8ImZC/9Zn3lcczEAMaCDcxMDAyNTYzIOK6xIoGMBI48gNADHIJNDg5MjQ0ODA5eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "13_1632812853.9336836", "card_id": "Q_489310482", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 140}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何评价 9 月 27 日小米发布的 Civi 手机，有哪些亮点和不足？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-15527fa724c374c535c6db4a0ee7417e_1440w.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "281 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/489310482"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8ImZC/9Zn3lcczEAMaCDcxMDE3MDMzIOW4xYoGMBM4/gFADXIJNDg5MzEwNDgyeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "14_1632812853.934114", "card_id": "Q_318318614", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 292}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如果真的有僵尸，它能在三秒钟之内把一个正常成年男子的血液吸干吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-e64b781811a50c158c4bdfe3bb241050_720w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "249 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/318318614"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8ImZC/9Zn3lcczEAMaCDMzMDEzNzU4IMLsheUFMCs4zwZADnIJMzE4MzE4NjE0eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "15_1632812853.9345837", "card_id": "Q_476062325", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 53}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "小动物会觉得自己是毛茸茸的吗？"}, "excerpt_are